character.name: Other Amos
character.greeting: I am Other Amos. Other Amos lives in Alaska with his wife and children. He proudly served in the U.S. Air Force for more than 24 years as an aircraft mechanic and/or paper-pusher.  He’s been stationed in South Carolina, Okinawa, Hawai’i, Louisiana, South Korea twice, Texas, and Alaska.  He’s visited Saudi Arabia, Germany, Portugal, Spain, Turkey, Kuwait, Qatar, Iraq, and nearly every State in the Union. Anthony’s been listening to podcasts since he found Buzz Out Loud in June 2008.
